"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-rendezvous-with-olympian-swimmer-elizabeth-lyon-beisel\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now  She is more to the firm and strict postures that she has posed in her pictures from the Olympics 2016.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A vibrant and down-to-earth personality with a whimsical sense of humor, Elizabeth Lyon Beisel is an American swimmer \\u00a0who specializes in backstroke and individual medley events.\", \"from\": 118, \"to\": 296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 191, \"end\": 200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9057051513582688, \"rank\": 0.10411195368423659, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 201, \"end\": 205, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"score\": 0.9999949775600431, \"rank\": 5.021741416249541e-06, \"text\": \"Lyon\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lyon\"}, {\"begin\": 219, \"end\": 227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999997151003706, \"rank\": 2.6239622684809554e-07, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beisel was placed second in the 400 m individual medley at the 2016 US Olympic Swimming Trials.\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She has won a total of nine medals in major international competitions such as Olympics, World Aquatics, and the Pan Pacific championships.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 507, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Pacific_Swimming_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.2290937387557223e-13, \"text\": \"Pan Pacific championships\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Pacific_Swimming_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pan_Pacific_Swimming_Championships\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She started surfing at a tender age of 10 and is an avid violin player.\", \"from\": 534, \"to\": 605, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having known that maharani meant queen in Nepali and that she shared her name with Queen Elizabeth II, she admired being called 'Maharani' throughout her visit in Nepal.\", \"from\": 606, \"to\": 775, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 648, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 0.9999998337680291, \"rank\": 1.339645441363712e-07, \"text\": \"Nepali\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 689, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999869076370801, \"rank\": 1.3091960362816805e-05, \"text\": \"Queen Elizabeth II\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 695, \"end\": 707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"score\": 0.9999999999863576, \"rank\": 1.3761255165897368e-11, \"text\": \"Elizabeth II\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_II\"}, {\"begin\": 735, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maharani\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maharaja\"}, {\"begin\": 769, \"end\": 774, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My City's Sonam Lama caught up with Elizabeth to talk about her visit to Nepal and experiences as an international swimmer.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 813, \"end\": 822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"score\": 0.9057051513582688, \"rank\": 0.10411195368423659, \"text\": \"Elizabeth\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elizabeth_Bennet\"}, {\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 855, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How was your first visit to Nepal?\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 930, \"end\": 935, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have plans to revisit?\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a completely different world.\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 1003, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I loved travelling here because you get to see a variety of cultures and we were completely immersed in that culture.\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1121, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We were not near anything western but it was just the pure Himalayan culture.\", \"from\": 1122, \"to\": 1199, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1181, \"end\": 1190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Himalayas\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5980570851965e-14, \"text\": \"Himalayan\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Himalayas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Himalayas\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being an athlete myself it was pretty physically demanding and even being an athlete it was still very tough trek to the Himalayas.\", \"from\": 1200, \"to\": 1331, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We came across so many inspiring things on the way and that was incredible and the entire trip was amazing.\", \"from\": 1332, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We shopped in Namche, brought trinkets for our family.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1494, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1454, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namche_Bazaar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Namche\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namche_Bazaar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Namche_Bazaar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The day after we woke up at 4 am, walked up to Kalapatthar and watched the sunrise over Everest and Aamadablam along with the fascinating tea house.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1643, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1542, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kala_Patthar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kalapatthar\", \"types\": [\"Q8502\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kala_Patthar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kala_Patthar\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, I eagerly look forward to revisiting Nepal next year.\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1702, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1686, \"end\": 1691, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How would you describe yourself as a person?\", \"from\": 1704, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a loud and friendly person.\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I work hard and try to have fun whatever I do.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am an adventurous person so I am fond of doing adventurous things with my friends.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Travelling is a huge passion of mine.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I love to travel places and meet people from different parts of the world.\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 2027, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I find this quote in Istanbul \\\"The world is like a book and if you never travel then you only ever read one page\\\" and I found it interesting.\", \"from\": 2028, \"to\": 2169, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2049, \"end\": 2057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\", \"score\": 0.9999997470627342, \"rank\": 2.473225830607214e-07, \"text\": \"Istanbul\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Istanbul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from travelling I love music and I am fond of playing violin.\", \"from\": 2170, \"to\": 2237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What drew you to swimming?\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Since our entire state was surrounded by water, my parents wanted me to learn how to swim just to be safe around the ocean.\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2390, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was an energetic child and was always keen at swimming.\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"My parents joined me up for the swim team when I was five years old.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2517, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At seven I started breaking records and I got qualified for my first national swim team at 13.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2612, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a long career till now and I am glad that I have gotten to travel the world and meet many people through it.\", \"from\": 2613, \"to\": 2733, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I make sure to work hard and give my best every time.\", \"from\": 2734, \"to\": 2787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What challenges do you often face as an Olympic swimmer?\", \"from\": 2789, \"to\": 2845, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think injuries are probably the most challenging when it comes to swimming.\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It requires you to be both physically and mentally healthy.\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 2984, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was injured about two years ago and I remember it was so hard because I wasn't necessarily depressed but I wasn't swimming fast and was not happy with myself.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think that is the side of sports that we hardly focus on.\", \"from\": 3146, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think to overcome an injury not only physically but also mentally is quite challenging.\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3295, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Any piece of advice you would like to give to our readers?\", \"from\": 3297, \"to\": 3355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It sounds a clich\\u00e9 but never give up on your dreams.\", \"from\": 3357, \"to\": 3409, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just because you are from Nepal does not mean that you can not be an Olympic swimmer.\", \"from\": 3410, \"to\": 3495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3436, \"end\": 3441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me it was just because I was from Rhode Island and I was short did not mean that I can not be a great swimmer.\", \"from\": 3497, \"to\": 3611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3535, \"end\": 3547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"score\": 0.9999954668194708, \"rank\": 4.1158411164066835e-06, \"text\": \"Rhode Island\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rhode_Island\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I always worked hard, dreamt big and kept competing and I think putting all those three things and then loving what you do is essential in order to be a good athlete.\", \"from\": 3612, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You do not have to be an Olympian, you can be an average swimmer but as long as you love it and you are having fun.\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3894, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3804, \"end\": 3812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999996784936, \"rank\": 3.2141946275724143e-10, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I think it's important to try something else other than what you often do.\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3970, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did violin and I think that was great for me because it helped balance my life.\", \"from\": 3971, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Try your hands in different things and figure out what you love.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4117, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ballot Box Revolt: What RSP's breakthrough victory...\", \"from\": 4119, \"to\": 4172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4143, \"end\": 4146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\", \"score\": 0.9999999521610345, \"rank\": 4.7838933324390045e-08, \"text\": \"RSP\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ryan_Seacrest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Warning, Threat or Opportunity?\", \"from\": 4174, \"to\": 4205, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nepal's major part...  Granary in crisis: Water politics leave Madhesh pa...  \\\"China stands ready to work with Nepal to carry forward the traditional friendship, deepen practical cooperation and advance bilateral relations\\\", read the statement.\", \"from\": 4206, \"to\": 4450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4206, \"end\": 4211, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 4285, \"end\": 4290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.999999447171529, \"rank\": 5.342653296259963e-07, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 4317, \"end\": 4322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Building Nepal's Digital Future  Fuel shortages in Nepal: A hidden threat to health a...  Second Innings of Balen and Gagan  Who will become Balen's climate pilot?\", \"from\": 4452, \"to\": 4615, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4503, \"end\": 4508, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.5371562163177494e-21, \"text\": \"Nepal\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nepal\"}, {\"begin\": 4560, \"end\": 4565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Balen\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0